			               													<description>From publisher blurb:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Have you ever wanted to play as your favorite monster in Pathfinder, but could not due to unbalanced abilities, the campaign being too low level, or worried that every town guardsman would attack you on sight?  Did you ever wish that the more iconic monsters had more interesting societies than primitive &amp;ldquo;kill or be killed&amp;rdquo; social orders?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you answered yes to any of these questions, then Playable Monsters Vol. 1: Fantasy Iconics &amp;amp; Mythology has what you&amp;rsquo;re looking for!  Included are PC-friendly versions of 16 monsters we grew to know and love from table-top role-playing and mythology!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play as a fire giant, belonging to a clan of proud descendants of a fallen empire!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Take the role of a naga, the sacred guardians of magical shrines and prisons of fell entities!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Be a doppelganger belonging to the Silent Stars, the mystical organization of lorekeepers tasked with finding forgotten knowledge and responsible for the creation of their race!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Turn your enemies to stone as a medusa, a humanoid transformed by the esoteric rites of the serpent cults!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Live life as a vampire, possessed of great power yet cursed with the prison of undeath!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;And much, much more!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You&amp;rsquo;ve GMed them, you fought them, but now it&amp;rsquo;s time to play as them!  Grab Playable Monsters if you want a fun and versatile assortment of classic monstrous races your gaming group is sure to enjoy!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
